Agyemang Diawusie (amụrụ na 12 Febụwarị 1998) bụ onye Germany na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-agba aka nri maka otu Austrian Bundesliga SV Ried Ọ bụbu onye ntorobịa Germany nke mba ụwa.
Mgbe ọ gbasịrị egwu na ngalaba ntorobịa nke SV Fortuna Regensburg, Diawusie kwagara na agụmakwụkwọ nke Jahn Regensburg
Na mmalite 2014 ọ sonyeere ndị otu n'okpuru-17 nke 1
FC Nürnberg, ebe ọ ga-eme ihe mgbaru ọsọ itoolu na egwuregwu 22 n'ime afọ na ọkara na-esote
Nke a dọtara uche nke mgbe ahụ 2
Bundesliga club RB Leipzig, bụ onye mesịrị debanye aha ya na free n'oge okpomọkụ nke 2015
Maka ndị Saxon, ọ na-egwu egwuregwu 48 na n'okpuru 19 Bundesliga wee nweta ihe mgbaru ọsọ 19
Na 2016, ya na ndị otu ahụ meriri Saxon Under-19 Cup
Na mgbakwunye, ejiri ya mee ihe ugboro atọ na otu nke abụọ nke Leipzig.
N'oge ọkọchị nke afọ 2017, RB Leipzig bịanyere aka na Diawusie na nkwekọrịta ọkachamara ruo n'afọ 2020 wee zigara ya na mgbazinye na 3
Klọb Liga SV Wehen Wiesbaden maka oge 2017 na afọ 18, ebe o nwere oge izizi siri ike na bọọlụ ọkachamara na goolu anọ na enyemaka iri na otu na egwuregwu iri atọ na ise.
Maka oge 2018 na 19, Diawusie alaghachighị na Leipzig, mana ọ kwagara na 2

Klọb Bundesliga FC Ingolstadt 04, ebe ọ bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta nke ga-aga ruo 30 June 2021. Mgbe ọ pụtara naanị otu ugboro tupu ezumike oyi, ọ laghachiri na SV Wehen Wiesbaden na mgbazinye na ngwụcha Jenụwarị 2019 ruo na ngwụchi oge. Diawusie pụtara ugboro iri na anọ maka ha na ọkara nke abụọ nke oge ahụ, ebe ọ gbara goolu abụọ ma nye enyemaka ise
SV Wehen Wiesbaden were ọnọdụ nke atọ wee zute FC Ingolstadt 04 na play-offs
Iji "chebe" Diawusie, a tọhapụrụ ya na SV Wehen Wiesbaden n'ihu egwuregwu relegation. Na play-offs, Wehen Wiesbaden meriri nkwalite na 2 Bundesliga
N'afọ 201920, Diawusie laghachiri na FC Ingolstadt 04, bụ ndị e wepụrụ na 3
